<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>One thing to keep in mind, the sooner you agro, the harder it is for a melee to pull the mob off you.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->This is not entirely true... it is for the most part though.<br>
